      "review_id": "HygHWpHH2m",
      "rebuttal_id": "HyghIbr50m",
      "sentence_index": 4,
      "text": "Yeh et al. (2017) use the discriminator loss of a trained GAN as an indicator of how realistic their restoration is.",
